{"tid":211191,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"抄到足！Instagram 用家發現大量照片被完美抄襲","createTime":"2017-04-21T12:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T13:07:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc12150e57e0f8d7cd8b8c7cd280553834b7ed29","tid":211191,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/instagrams-800x478.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2Finstagrams-800x478.jpg&h=730faf1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在 Instagram 上找到相似構圖的照片並不難，尤其在旅遊聖地之類，總會有差不多的照片。不過如果有人把一連串的旅遊照片都抄襲拍攝，感覺就有點可怕了。<br />\n<br />\n事源 Jack Morris (@doyoutravel) 和 Lauren Bullen (@gypsea_lust) 是 Instagram 上的人氣旅遊攝影師，追隨者多達 200 萬，而最近Lauren 發現其中一個追隨者的照片，與她自己的照片非常相像，而且不只是一張，意思所有照片無論拍攝地添、構圖、顏色、衣着，甚至標題都一模一樣，只是相中人物換了別人而已，也意味着他們的行程和旅遊地點也被那人跟隨。<br />\n<br />\n這個程度的抄襲已經超越了一般的抄襲，根本就是在模仿攝影師的一切，讓她感到有點驚恐。雖然說照片是重新拍攝，不能說是侵犯版權，但這樣的行爲仍然令原創者感到不安。然而換個角度想，能夠做到這個程度的「致敬」，也可以算是一種成就了吧。<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/comparison1-800x490.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2Fcomparison1-800x490.jpg&h=3af58cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/comparison2-800x530.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2Fcomparison2-800x530.jpg&h=69d1d9aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/comparison3-800x608.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2Fcomparison3-800x608.jpg&h=c6e6d448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/comparison15-800x633.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2Fcomparison15-800x633.jpg&h=78fe5cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2016/11/13/someone-follows-around-world-copy-photos/dc/photogism/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2016%2F11%2F13%2Fsomeone-follows-around-world-copy-photos%2Fdc%2Fphotogism%2F&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=d68fe6fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2016/11/13/someone-follows-around-world-copy-photos/dc/photogism/</a>"},{"pid":"b4362f6f5b145a985582c6965013ca7596aae8e2","tid":211191,"uid":20110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:54:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6d8bdaced1c387dd342f97c78a0e493086fac95","tid":211191,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:55:25.000Z","msg":"樓主衰咩？"},{"pid":"7d31ab3be6c33e8bf996da7ed7e756cd88ab4c7e","tid":211191,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:56:56.000Z","msg":"香港大把"},{"pid":"3763746939a7f8a212ea6ebfda3add92882e59ec","tid":211191,"uid":414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:57:37.000Z","msg":"單新聞都幾個月前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf30e17e5b1af292917655f5dde2ffb6323a491","tid":211191,"uid":6153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:01:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9fcd06c94d8947a3eb8a781cd9c5b7a35bc9f6c1","tid":211191,"uid":41611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:05:18.000Z","msg":"好似有部份做內容農場既admin轉做呢啲<br />\n至於具體點賺錢就唔太清楚"},{"pid":"58f31db3db72ea0e705fd7e63ee3d97a045acc51","tid":211191,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:07:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}